INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (132001, '…but he realized he would never reconcile himself to life as something other than a prelude. What’s life’s meaning then? What is it? What does make the world go round, not letting hope die? What do people dream about, watching the endless flow of years? They dream. A dream, that’s it. We live for our only dream, which can lead us, hand in hand, through our life; for the dream we reconcile ourselves to any frustrations and we shall struggle for releasing its silky wings from the net of reality. (The right to a mistake.)', 6213, 0), (132002, 'Smartass Disciple: Master, how do I know that I am not dreaming right now ?Master of Stupidity: You don’t. Only those who see you''re dreaming can tell it.', 1296, 0), (132003, 'Sober Minds give the world a chance. True Love brings you Hope. Blind Faith moves mountains. And the main savior from despair is Laughter.', 6213, 0), (132004, 'tears,love,life	Who knows how many tears have flown in the Word of God from the creation of the world?', 3575, 0), (132005, 'The universe, they say, depended for its operation on the balance of four forces which they identified as charm, persuasion, uncertainty, and bloody-mindedness.', 195, 0), (132006, 'I enjoy it when the world smiles; the more smiles, the warmer I am.', 2610, 0), (132007, 'I''m a lion in a strange land.', 230, 0), (132008, 'Somewhere in this small world, you can find a place where everyone appreciates you more than you think you deserve.', 4238, 0), (132009, 'The world is a navy in an empty ocean.', 2610, 0), (132010, 'Sex and violence ... are the two great engines of the world.', 25266, 0), (132011, 'It’s funny. From up here, the destruction seems to fade. Almost as if like people, in time, even the world can heal itself.', 8253, 0), (132012, 'Candace doesn''t have to worry about me being busy in my world without you, because you are my world.', 17433, 0), (132013, 'Do you see this egg? With this you can topp