 his Jeep, looked him dead in the eye and kissed him. He asked if he could come up, and I just walked up the steps and said, not yet. That was the moment I knew I loved him.', 3805, 0), (133384, 'You''re no better. Playing dress-up like you know right from wrong. Who made you the fucking hero?I did.', 25433, 0), (133385, 'Sometimes the anxiety takes over and I can’t seem to fathom the love he gives me.', 3805, 0), (133386, 'When I''m with you,I feel exposed.Naked. When I''m naked with you, I feel clothed.Sheltered.', 3588, 0), (133387, 'They tell us the only way to move on is to forget.“Forgive,” they say.Realise that you deserve better.That maybe they deserve better.You can''t fight fire with fire.Extinguish it once and for all."Do not look back," they say.They don''t tell you that only one thing is needed. Only one:love.When you are filled to the brim with love,you only emanate love.You become lover and love itself.Only then will you love even the very people you wish to hate.', 3588, 0), (133388, 'You know how sometimes you meet someone and you feel like you''ve known them your whole life?Well, I feel like I''ve loved you my whole life.', 3588, 0), (133389, 'Please don’t be upset. The last thing in the world I want is to see you upset and that too with me. It’s terrifying to see your beautiful eyes turn red with anger.', 14827, 0), (133390, 'The miraculous power of love has often been underestimated just like we underestimate the power of sleep. Most of the herculean tasks performed by men were possible because they had been deeply in love and had slept well the night before.', 14827, 0), (133391, 'Let’s face it. There are good people and bad people everywhere. Illiteracy, poor education, wars, greed , corruption and similar factors were responsible for the problems in both India and Pakistan. Religious fanatics benefited from these factors and developed formidable socio-political strongholds in both countries.', 14827, 0), (133392, 'It is your ego that needs to 