ality... The whole time you''ve been wanting to hear the right thing from a person that will stop you.', 7384, 0), (133867, 'Each day''s dawn is a sweet symphony and as long as I hear the music, my dreams will have to die another day.', 25507, 0), (133868, 'We are the result of millions of years of evolution, people died to offer us the chance to have a better life and here''s what we did of it all !We didn''t even realized that freedom, nowadays, is nothing more than an illusion. We are the slaves of money, of economy, of lobbies, medias and time.Our thoughts and dreams are our only freedom.', 20570, 0), (133869, 'Nothing you build will ever last without a lot of tender-loving-care (TLC).', 3337, 0), (133870, 'In fairy tales the evil characters disappear or die, in reality, evil spreads while you wait for your hero on a horse, only to realise the sword to save yourself was always in your hand...', 4800, 0), (133871, 'Remember to live and learn to give.', 2586, 0), (133872, 'Give much, demand little.', 2586, 0), (133873, 'The more you give, the more you will have to give.', 2586, 0), (133874, 'When we spend money we lose them forever, when we give them away, we will have them forever.', 2586, 0), (133875, 'Give away everything to have it forever.', 2586, 0), (133876, 'Don''t give a gift with expectation to get but if you have got a gift always try to give.', 2586, 0), (133877, 'When you give without expectation, you will always have more to give away.', 2586, 0), (133878, 'The more you give, the more you will have the ability to give.', 2586, 0), (133879, 'You never can give without receiving it.', 2586, 0), (133880, 'Give with love, give with smile, give freely, it is our duty and responsibility to humanity.', 2586, 0), (133881, 'Generosity is the flower of our love for the humanity.', 2586, 0), (133882, 'The joy of giving last forever.So give with love and forget it never.', 2586, 0), (133883, 'Serve a person in need.Give generously indeed.', 2586, 0), (133884, 'To have more, give moreTo be happy, love more.', 2586, 0), (133885, 'Giving and receiving are the same process. You are the conduit playing your role.', 2586, 0), (133886, 'It isn''t important how much you are giving but it is very important that you are giving.', 2586, 0), (133887, 'Generosity is not only giving but also a sign of caring.', 2586, 0), (133888, 'More often than not, how you give is more important than what you give.', 2586, 0), (133889, 'She''s a sailboat and I''m an anchor, pulling us both down.', 73, 0), (133890, 'Put all your pain on a piece of paper, write it all down, every experience, every ache, every hurtful moment. Then take a match, and set fire to that piece of paper. All the hurt you have inside you is burning just as it burnt inside of you, until it is completely gone. From this moment forward you are free. Nothing can harm you. No past. No present. No future. You are reborn into water, and nothing in the entirety of this world can set fire to water, nor crush it. Whatever pressures you face, you will float. Whatever tries to sink you, you will rise up. Today, right now, in this moment, you are a warrior. Now smile, it will set fire to those who sought to burn you...', 4800, 0), (133891, 'We all have problems, but let''s not kid ourselves: it''s how we deal with them that makes the difference.', 10046, 0), (133892, 'Give yourself without expecting any return.', 2586, 0), (133893, 'Some people are lucky to find love, others must settle with being liked...', 4800, 0), (133894, 'With the world now a global village, your vision has to transcend different races and faces in different places around the world.', 24838, 0), (133895, 'But you should know that about Dauntless- girl, guy, whatever, it doesn''t matter here. What matters is what you''ve got in your gut.', 73, 0), (133896, 'Well when my death is in front, I just want to turn back to my life, And say the last thing, looking in to its lens that, “Life oh my life, Nobody would have ever painted this life as beautiful as i did”. Good Bye-Ravi', 25508, 0), (133897, 'My late husband and I started our sons off as readers at a very young age. Today, they are voracious readers.', 24623, 0), (133898, 'A little hope and love now and thenWise and beautiful, more than often.', 2586, 0), (133899, 'Hope is the light, which shows the way of life.', 2586, 0), (133900, 'A baby is the symbol of the future, hope for the future, and our opinion in the future.', 2586, 0);
