d never coming out.', 1534, 0), (133979, 'Real smart begins when you quit quoting other people.', 30, 0), (133980, 'You are to me like white islands, in a world of vast darkness.', 523, 0), (133981, 'Never give up hope! If you do, you be dead already.', 25517, 0), (133982, 'The only reason a true friend won''t be there to pick you up is because they are lying beneath you from trying to break your fall.', 15127, 0), (133983, 'I bruise easily and sometimes I can’t stop bleeding.', 1534, 0), (133984, 'Extraordinary what the body remembers. The bones loded with love, grief silting the arteries, fear the bowels'' recurring mould. Who would have thought mere flesh and blood could hold so much of psyche''s ghostly script?', 12836, 0), (133985, 'Pessimism is the key to see what really goes on within our world, the lies and manipulation that circles us all is exposed', 25518, 0), (133986, 'life is like a teabag; you end up dead, replaced and forgotten.', 25519, 0), (133987, 'Time and Tide wait for no Man', 25520, 0), (133988, 'our love likestepping on to a planesitting down in a carwalking on unknown land will either take us to where we belongor throw us into darkness', 25481, 0), (133989, 'When you have those moments just think of me, call or text me when you feel weak and I will always be there for you. Nothing about this will be easy, life is hard, we just feel it more than most because our souls have been broken and are raw.', 25521, 0), (133990, 'Behold my Love which traveled by Sudden Days. I wash away my withered cold Hands to a Warm Embrace of You, My Eternal Summer!', 25522, 0), (133991, 'Corruption free" will truly be in a future impossible tense because many people re-elect unscrupulous politicians!In the end because of blind immunity to reality and impunity of "justified" corruptions in the government, it is always the hard working, suffering, struggling, less privileged citizens who are all the sacrificial lamb in times of disaster and calamities through their well catered embezzlement system.', 15605, 0), (133992, 'You’ve got to have confidence in the very thing that makes you unique – then wait for the world to catch up', 22683, 0), (133993, 'Find something you love and go for it with all your heart. No excuses, no plan B. Never settle for anything less than you know you can do.It will be hard, but I promise it will be worth it.', 523, 0), (133994, 'Little girls get hurt when they play grown-up games.', 801, 0), (133995, 'Independence means.. enjoying freedom and empowering others too to let them do so.', 11145, 0), (133996, 'He might be faithless but I believe in him.', 702, 0), (133997, 'No thanky-you; you can''t overcome hatred with more hatred. Force can kill the liar but not the lie, the hater but not the hate, and the violent but not the violence. Hate begets hate, violence begets violence, and war begets war.', 11668, 0), (133998, 'There''s so much to learn. So much to enjoy. So terribly much to be curious about. Take your life and run with it. Make a habit of being alive. This much of anything, I have learned. And am still learning.', 23450, 0), (133999, 'I think as a society we forget that men also have daddy issues, they''ve also had bad childhoods, they''re vulnerable beings.. They also need love. We are made to think men don''t have a hard time, and that''s mainly because we''ve trained them not to show emotion, not to shed a tear.. but I can assure you, we men break down just like every other being. We get depressed. We get heartbroken, we get scared, lonely, butterflies.. We feel every emotion just as women do.', 25481, 0), (134000, 'As an author, I want to write what I’m inspired to write. Not what my readers want me to write. I feel like the books will ultimately be better if my heart is fully into what I’m writing.', 316, 0);
